name: Beckoned Skull Archfiend
desc:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
This card's name becomes "Summoned Skull" while on the field, but it is still treated as an "Archfiend" card. Your opponent cannot target "Summoned Skull" you control with card effects. If this Synchro Summoned card you control is sent to your GY by your opponent's card: You can Special Summon 1 "Summoned Skull" from your hand, Deck, or GY.
